Management thru the Local Disaster Risk Reduction Management Office to:
a. include in the LDRRM Investment Plan, the establishment of toilets for PWDs as well as an appropriate storage area in their designated evacuation center;
b. Establish alternative sources of water supply for the evacuation center;
c. Provide enough space for the community kitchen so that it can accommodate plenty of evacuees ; and
d. Establish breastfeeding area or lactation area.

